pdate your KafkaConnect CR

Add this block under spec.template.pod
spec:
  template:
    pod:
      env:
        - name: CERTS_STORE_PASSWORD
          valueFrom:
            secretKeyRef:
              name: dev-kafka-cluster-cluster-ca-cert
              key: ca.password

